A simple PHP client for RESTful Metrics. See http://www.restfulmetrics.com

NOTE: 
There are a few class constants in Client.php that can be used for configuration purposes. 

USAGE:

require '[PATH/TO]/RestfulMetrics/Client.php';
$rm = new RestfulMetrics_Client([APIKEY], [APP_ID]);
$rm->addMetric("simple", 1);
$rm->addMetric("compound", array("a", "b", "c"));

VERSION:
0.2
